snippet.title: FINAL FANTASY XV: EPISODE IGNIS- Yasunori Mitsuda Guest Composer Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/final-fantasy-xv-ps4/

We are thrilled to reveal Yasunori Mitsuda as the guest composer for FINAL FANTASY XV: EPISODE IGNIS! Mitsuda, renowned for his work in Chrono Trigger, shares his excitement to be working with FINAL FANTASY for the first time. Tune in to hear more! 

Available through the Season Pass or buy individually in the PlayStation Store.

https://store.playstation.com/#!/games/addons/final-fantasy-xv-season-pass/cid=UP0082-CUSA01633_00-FFXVSEASONPASS00

http://www.finalfantasyxv.com/
